Here’s a comprehensive list of CSS topics categorized for easy reference:

---

### **1. Basics of CSS**
- What is CSS?
- Syntax (Selectors, Properties, Values)
- Types of CSS (Inline, Internal, External)
- Comments in CSS

---

### **2. Selectors**
- Universal Selector (`*`)
- Type Selector (Element selectors)
- Class Selector (`.class`)
- ID Selector (`#id`)
- Grouping Selectors (`,`)
- Descendant, Child, Adjacent Sibling, General Sibling Selectors
- Attribute Selectors

---

### **3. Colors and Backgrounds**
- Color formats (HEX, RGB, RGBA, HSL, HSLA)
- Background properties (`background-color`, `background-image`, `background-repeat`, `background-size`, `background-position`, `background-attachment`)
- Gradients (Linear and Radial)

---

### **4. Box Model**
- Components (Margin, Border, Padding, Content)
- Box-sizing (`content-box`, `border-box`)

---

### **5. Text and Fonts**
- Font properties (`font-family`, `font-size`, `font-style`, `font-weight`)
- Text properties (`color`, `text-align`, `text-decoration`, `text-transform`, `letter-spacing`, `word-spacing`, `line-height`, `white-space`)
- Google Fonts Integration

---

### **6. Layouts**
- Display Types (`inline`, `block`, `inline-block`, `none`)
- Positioning (`static`, `relative`, `absolute`, `fixed`, `sticky`)
- Float and Clear
- Z-index
- Overflow (`visible`, `hidden`, `scroll`, `auto`)

---

### **7. Flexbox**
- Container properties (`display: flex`, `flex-direction`, `justify-content`, `align-items`, `align-content`, `flex-wrap`)
- Item properties (`flex`, `order`, `align-self`)

---

### **8. CSS Grid**
- Container properties (`display: grid`, `grid-template-rows`, `grid-template-columns`, `gap`, `grid-auto-rows`, `grid-auto-columns`)
- Item properties (`grid-row`, `grid-column`, `grid-area`)

---

### **9. Responsive Design**
- Media Queries
- Mobile-first vs Desktop-first approach
- Units (Relative: `%`, `em`, `rem`, `vh`, `vw`; Absolute: `px`, `cm`, etc.)
- Viewport meta tag

---

### **10. Transitions and Animations**
- Transitions (`transition-property`, `transition-duration`, `transition-timing-function`, `transition-delay`)
- Keyframes (`@keyframes`, `animation-name`, `animation-duration`, `animation-timing-function`, `animation-delay`, `animation-iteration-count`, `animation-direction`)

---

### **11. Pseudo-classes and Pseudo-elements**
- Pseudo-classes (`:hover`, `:focus`, `:nth-child()`, `:first-child`, etc.)
- Pseudo-elements (`::before`, `::after`, `::placeholder`, etc.)

---

### **12. Advanced CSS**
- Variables (Custom Properties: `--var-name`)
- CSS Functions (`calc()`, `clamp()`, `min()`, `max()`)
- CSS Specificity and Inheritance
- Shorthand Properties
- CSS Resets and Normalize.css

---

### **13. Visual Effects**
- Shadows (`box-shadow`, `text-shadow`)
- Opacity
- Clip-path
- Filters (`blur()`, `brightness()`, `contrast()`, etc.)

---

### **14. CSS Frameworks (Optional)**
- Introduction to frameworks like Bootstrap, Tailwind CSS

---

### **15. CSS with Preprocessors (Optional)**
- Introduction to SASS/SCSS
- Variables, Nesting, Mixins, Partials, Extend

